### Testing AJAX Handlers

**AJAX Test Setup:**

```php
public function test_ajax_load_more_posts() {
    // Create test posts
    $post_ids = $this->factory->post->create_many(5);

    // Set up AJAX request
    $_POST['action'] = 'load_more_posts';
