## Advanced Patterns

### Concurrent Testing

```typescript
import { describe, it, expect } from 'vitest';

describe.concurrent('Parallel Tests', () => {
  it('test 1', async () => {
    await slowOperation();
    expect(true).toBe(true);
  });

