  }
}
```

❌ **Forgetting to await async tests**:
```typescript
// WRONG - test passes before assertion
it('fetches data', () => {
  fetchData().then(data => {
    expect(data).toBeDefined();  // Never runs!
  });
});

// CORRECT
it('fetches data', async () => {
  const data = await fetchData();
  expect(data).toBeDefined();
});
```

❌ **Not cleaning up mocks**:
```typescript
